<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" media="screen" href="/~d/styles/rss2full.xsl"?><?xml-stylesheet type="text/css" media="screen" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~d/styles/itemcontent.css"?><rss xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:wfw="http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:sy="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/" xmlns:slash="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/" version="2.0"><channel><title>UNWIRE.HK</title><link>https://unwire.hk</link><description /><lastBuildDate>Wed, 17 Nov 2021 08:43:14 +0000</lastBuildDate><language>zh-TW</language><sy:updatePeriod>hourly	</sy:updatePeriod><sy:updateFrequency>1	</sy:updateFrequency><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml" href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/unwirelife" /><feedburner:info xmlns:feedburner="http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0" uri="unwirelife" /><atom10:link xmlns:atom10="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" rel="hub" href="http://pubsubhubbub.appspot.com/" /><item><title>先達 13 部手機 20 秒被偷走   50 歲手機賊涉 iPhone 13 Pro Max 失竊案</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/11/17/13-iphone-13-pro-max-got-stolen/hottopic/spotlight/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=13-iphone-13-pro-max-got-stolen</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 17 Nov 2021 08:43:14 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[城中熱話]]></category><category><![CDATA[iPhone 13 Pro Max]]></category><category><![CDATA[先達]]></category><category><![CDATA[盜竊]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1071863</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>日前旺角先達廣場手機舖發生盜竊事件，有賊人假冒職員，公然偷走 13 部 iPhone 13 Pro Max。警 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">日前旺角先達廣場手機舖發生盜竊事件，有賊人假冒職員，公然偷走 13 部 iPhone 13 Pro Max。警方其後在葵涌拘捕一名 50 歲男子，涉及 5 宗店舖盜竊案。針對手機電器鋪的盜竊案件，被盜手機共 17 部，總值約 16 萬元。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1071864" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/9764EA7E-1A9D-41C0-B1E4-5C685754E1EE-694x371.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="371" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/9764EA7E-1A9D-41C0-B1E4-5C685754E1EE-694x371.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/9764EA7E-1A9D-41C0-B1E4-5C685754E1EE-1280x684.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/9764EA7E-1A9D-41C0-B1E4-5C685754E1EE-768x410.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/9764EA7E-1A9D-41C0-B1E4-5C685754E1EE-1536x820.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/9764EA7E-1A9D-41C0-B1E4-5C685754E1EE.jpeg 1569w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1071867" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/077DF41F-10A5-40FD-A181-E03366740CAA-694x373.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="373" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/077DF41F-10A5-40FD-A181-E03366740CAA-694x373.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/077DF41F-10A5-40FD-A181-E03366740CAA-1280x687.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/077DF41F-10A5-40FD-A181-E03366740CAA-768x412.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/077DF41F-10A5-40FD-A181-E03366740CAA-1536x825.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/077DF41F-10A5-40FD-A181-E03366740CAA.jpeg 1568w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>（圖片來源：香港 01）</p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">據該店店主透露，15 日下午有客人到舖頭出售 13 部 iPhone 13 Pro Max 256GB 手機，因店鋪現款不足，他便將手機放上貨架後，到另一舖頭取款。他離開後舖頭 2 分鐘內，竟有一名賊人公然打開舖頭櫃門，在客人面前掃走貨架上的手機，犯案時間僅 20 秒。黃先生亦指出，賊人在進入店舖前曾與客人進行對話，令客人誤以為該賊人是手機舖職員。事後黃先生並未立即發現手機被盜，直接將尾款交給客人，客人離去後才發現手機全數被偷走。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1071865" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/0FC1F28F-42F6-444D-8DC6-C45415DAE413-694x464.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="464" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/0FC1F28F-42F6-444D-8DC6-C45415DAE413-694x464.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/0FC1F28F-42F6-444D-8DC6-C45415DAE413-1280x855.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/0FC1F28F-42F6-444D-8DC6-C45415DAE413-768x513.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/0FC1F28F-42F6-444D-8DC6-C45415DAE413-1536x1026.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/0FC1F28F-42F6-444D-8DC6-C45415DAE413.jpeg 1576w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /> <img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1071866" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/9F34B602-C1C5-404F-9939-4F4C852F413D-694x456.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="456" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/9F34B602-C1C5-404F-9939-4F4C852F413D-694x456.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/9F34B602-C1C5-404F-9939-4F4C852F413D-1280x841.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/9F34B602-C1C5-404F-9939-4F4C852F413D-768x505.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/9F34B602-C1C5-404F-9939-4F4C852F413D-1536x1010.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/9F34B602-C1C5-404F-9939-4F4C852F413D.jpeg 1576w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">警方在同日（15 日）拘捕一名 50 歲男子，涉嫌與旺角先達廣場的 iPhone 13 Pro Max 失竊案有關。警方在今年 10 至 11 月期間接獲 5 宗發生於油尖旺區，針對手機電器鋪的盜竊案件，被盜手機共 17 部，總值約 16 萬元。據悉被捕男子為單人犯案，以顧客身份進入店舖，剪斷連接手機的保安裝置，或直接偷走手機。警方油尖警區刑事調查隊第 7 隊主管陳君圖表示，疑犯為無業中國籍男子，將被落案起訴 5 項盜竊罪，明日於九龍裁判法院提堂。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：</span><a href="https://www.hk01.com/突發/701781/先達 20 秒擸 iphone 肥賊落網-偷 17 部共-16 萬手機-將被控 5 項盜竊罪#media_id=7882424"><span style="font-weight: 400;"> 香港 01</span></a></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 : </span><a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
