</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>立法會票站設光學標記閱讀機，確認投選人數無誤</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/11/17/election-related-activities-in-respect-of-the-legislative-council-election/hottopic/spotlight/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=election-related-activities-in-respect-of-the-legislative-council-election</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 17 Nov 2021 07:47:03 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[城中熱話]]></category><category><![CDATA[光學標記閱讀機]]></category><category><![CDATA[立法會]]></category><category><![CDATA[立法會換屆選舉]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1071847</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>立法會換屆選舉將於十二月舉行，今屆立法會新增 40 個選舉委員會界別議席，由選委會的選委以「全票式」選出，每名 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">立法會換屆選舉將於十二月舉行，今屆立法會新增 40 個選舉委員會界別議席，由選委會的選委以「全票式」選出，每名選委必須投選不多於亦不少於 40 人。為確認投選人數是否有誤，選管會主席馮驊表示票站將設有光學標記閱讀機，投票時間亦延至 8 時半展開。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1071850" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/87A3F0DF-276D-4E0B-8AD4-30149E1879AA-694x371.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="371" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/87A3F0DF-276D-4E0B-8AD4-30149E1879AA-694x371.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/87A3F0DF-276D-4E0B-8AD4-30149E1879AA-1280x684.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/87A3F0DF-276D-4E0B-8AD4-30149E1879AA-768x411.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/87A3F0DF-276D-4E0B-8AD4-30149E1879AA-1536x821.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/87A3F0DF-276D-4E0B-8AD4-30149E1879AA-2048x1095.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/87A3F0DF-276D-4E0B-8AD4-30149E1879AA.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>（圖片來源：選管會）</p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">馮驊表示，光學標記閱讀機不會記錄或點算選票上的選擇，為免選民因誤選多於或少於 40 人而導致該選票無效，選舉委員會界別投票站內提供的光學標記閱讀機，為供選民檢查選票上所選取的候選人是否 40 名；他亦鼓勵選民先使用光學標記閱讀機確認準確後才放入投票箱。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1071848" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/CDE2564B-AB55-44CC-8E7A-B809320A5D00-694x379.jpeg" alt="" width="694" height="379" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/CDE2564B-AB55-44CC-8E7A-B809320A5D00-694x379.jpeg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/CDE2564B-AB55-44CC-8E7A-B809320A5D00-1280x699.jpeg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/CDE2564B-AB55-44CC-8E7A-B809320A5D00-768x419.jpeg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/CDE2564B-AB55-44CC-8E7A-B809320A5D00-1536x838.jpeg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/CDE2564B-AB55-44CC-8E7A-B809320A5D00-2048x1118.jpeg 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/CDE2564B-AB55-44CC-8E7A-B809320A5D00.jpeg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>（圖片來源：香港電台）</p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">今年九月舉行的選委會選舉亦採用光學閱讀機設備點票，但期間出現光標機「卡紙」等情況，四千多張選票，結果共耗 14 小時才完成點票。有報告認為，用光學標記閱讀機點票時，部分選票或未有疊齊，而出現「卡紙」。馮驊強調，地方選區或功能界別選民在填劃選票後，不可摺疊選票放入投票箱；而選委會界別選民的選票，亦不可摺疊，並要放入封套內，再放入投票箱。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：</span><a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1616483-20211022.htm"><span style="font-weight: 400;"> 香港電台</span></a></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 : </span><a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
