</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>【教學】Disney+ GroupWatch 教學，多部裝置同步睇戲</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/11/17/disney-plus-groupwatch/wireless-home/audio-visual/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=disney-plus-groupwatch</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 17 Nov 2021 04:33:53 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[影音產品]]></category><category><![CDATA[生活娛樂]]></category><category><![CDATA[電影 / 劇集]]></category><category><![CDATA[Disney]]></category><category><![CDATA[GroupWatch]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1071638</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>同朋友一齊去戲院睇戲固然開心，不過在家中一樣都可同身處異地的朋友共享睇戲樂趣。今日正式在香港投入服務的 Dis [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>同朋友一齊去戲院睇戲固然開心，不過在家中一樣都可同身處異地的朋友共享睇戲樂趣。今日正式在香港投入服務的 Disney+ 就內置有 GroupWatch 功能，讓兩人或以上 Disney+ 用戶，分隔異地仍可一齊收看相同影片的同一個畫面，更可即時共享你的睇片感受。Disney+ GroupWatch 功能可同步參與者的影片播放時間軸，確保所有人都在看同一畫面，例如有一位參與者想去廁所，可大家一齊暫停畫面；大家想飛到某段劇情一看再看，任何一個人操作播放時間軸，所有人都會跳到該段劇情。以下將會介紹 GroupWatch 的詳細用法。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-16-20.45.59.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1071668" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/螢幕截圖-2021-11-16-20.45.59.jpg" alt="" width="535" height="578" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0036-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1071674" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0036-1-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0036-1-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0036-1-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0036-1-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0036-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0004-5.jpg"><br /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0024-4.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1071670" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0024-4-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0024-4-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0024-4-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0024-4.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>Disney+ 的 GroupWatch 功能主要用上播放時間軸（或叫播放進度條）「同步處理」方式，確保每一位參與者都可播放同一段影片的同一秒畫面。好處是不限裝置平台種類，不論每個人用的是 iPhone、Android 手機、智能電視或電腦，只要任何人能登入 Disney+，都可參與 GroupWatch 大家一同收看影片。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0008-5.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1071650" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0008-5-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0008-5-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0008-5-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0008-5.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲「同步群組」動作保持大家觀看同一個畫面</p><h2>建立 GroupWatch 影片邀請朋友一齊睇</h2><p>首先不得不讚 Disney+，它這個 GroupWatch 其實不限帳戶種類、不限播放平台。只要是兩部不同的裝置，就算是同一個 Disney+ 帳戶，甚至同一個 Disney+「使用者」都可用 GroupWatch 一齊睇片。例如你有兩部裝置，都用相同帳戶、相同「使用者」登入，兩部機就可玩 GroupWatch：你可以一部機在客廳電視睇戲，而仔仔在房間內的電腦，都可參與你的 GroupWatch 一齊睇戲。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0019-3.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1071654" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0019-3-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0019-3-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0019-3-416x900.jpg 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0019-3-768x1663.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0019-3-709x1536.jpg 709w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0019-3-946x2048.jpg 946w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0019-3.jpg 739w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></a></p><h2></h2><h2>Step 1</h2><p>在任何一款裝置打開 Disney+ 應用程式或網頁，打開想看的影片，在影片介紹頁面，點擊 GroupWatch 按鈕。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0009-3-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1071656" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0009-3-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0009-3-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0009-3-416x900.jpg 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0009-3-768x1661.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0009-3-710x1536.jpg 710w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0009-3-947x2048.jpg 947w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0009-3-scaled.jpg 739w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></a></p><h2>Step 2</h2><p>進入圖中的 GroupWatch 介面，想邀請你的朋友，按「＋邀請」按鈕；</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0008-6-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1071657" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0008-6-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0008-6-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0008-6-416x900.jpg 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0008-6-768x1661.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0008-6-710x1536.jpg 710w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0008-6-947x2048.jpg 947w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0008-6-scaled.jpg 739w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0007-5-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1071658" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0007-5-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0007-5-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0007-5-416x900.jpg 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0007-5-768x1661.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0007-5-710x1536.jpg 710w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0007-5-947x2048.jpg 947w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0007-5-scaled.jpg 739w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></a></p><h2>Step 3</h2><p>在 iOS/Android 分享畫面中，選擇你想分享的對象。可選擇利用 WhatsApp、Facebook Messenger，甚至電郵發出你的邀請。例如選了 FB Messenger，再選擇對象便可。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0006-1-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1071659" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0006-1-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0006-1-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0006-1-416x900.jpg 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0006-1-768x1661.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0006-1-710x1536.jpg 710w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0006-1-947x2048.jpg 947w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0006-1-scaled.jpg 739w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></a>▲先選取分享之方式，可選 WhatsApp、Messenger 等等，如果是鄰近朋友，更可以直接 AirDrop<a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0005-3-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1071660" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0005-3-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0005-3-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0005-3-416x900.jpg 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0005-3-768x1661.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0005-3-710x1536.jpg 710w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0005-3-947x2048.jpg 947w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0005-3-scaled.jpg 739w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></a>▲再選取你希望分享的對象</p><h2></h2><h2>Step 4 以下是收到邀請者的操作</h2><p>這樣你會傳送一個邀請出去。當你的朋友收到邀請，打開連結。如果你是電腦用家，直接在瀏覽器打開邀請便可。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0004-6.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1071661" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0004-6-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0004-6-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0004-6-416x900.jpg 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0004-6-768x1663.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0004-6-709x1536.jpg 709w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0004-6-946x2048.jpg 946w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0004-6.jpg 739w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></a></p><p>如果你是手機用家，並用 WhatsApp 分享，被邀者點擊連結就會打開 Disney+，你要選擇加入的「使用者」。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0003-5.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1071662" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0003-5-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0003-5-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0003-5-416x900.jpg 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0003-5-768x1663.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0003-5-709x1536.jpg 709w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0003-5-946x2048.jpg 946w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0003-5.jpg 739w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></a></p><h2>Facebook Messenger 獨有問題解決方法</h2><p>FB Messenger 會用內置瀏覽器打開邀請連結，你需要在圖中藍圈轉轉轉的畫面時，迅速地右下角分享按鈕；再於分享選單揀「在 Safari 開啟」。實際上手機不會用 Safari 開啟連結，而是會自動幫你打開 Disney+ 應用程式，此時你可選擇觀看影片的「使用者」。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0017.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1071663" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0017-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0017-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0017-416x900.jpg 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0017-768x1661.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0017-710x1536.jpg 710w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0017-947x2048.jpg 947w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0017.jpg 740w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></a>▲如果你是 FB Messenger 用戶，打開連結後會用內置瀏覽器開啟，你要在此藍圈轉轉的畫面，迅速按畫面右下角分享按鈕</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0016-5.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1071665" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0016-5-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0016-5-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0016-5-416x900.jpg 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0016-5-768x1663.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0016-5-709x1536.jpg 709w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0016-5-946x2048.jpg 946w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0016-5.jpg 739w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></a>▲在藍圈轉轉消失前，迅速地按「在 Safari 開啟」按鈕<a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0016-4.jpg"><br /></a></p><h2>Step 5 以下為群主的操作</h2><p>進入 GroupWatch+ 群組後，群主就可按「開始串流播放按鈕」去片。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0010-5-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1071666" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0010-5-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0010-5-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0010-5-416x900.jpg 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0010-5-768x1661.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0010-5-710x1536.jpg 710w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0010-5-947x2048.jpg 947w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0010-5-scaled.jpg 739w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></a>▲群主看見朋友加入，齊人後，可按「開始串流播放」按鈕</p><h2>Step 6</h2><p>然後大家都會一齊收看同一影片。之不過我們在實際試用後，發現同步處理並不超級準確，測試的兩部裝置有 1/3 至 1/2 秒差距，但實際應用上這一點的誤差應不會造成太大問題吧。如誤差太大，可移動一下播放時間軸再次同步，直至滿意為止。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0013-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1071651" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0013-2-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0013-2-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0013-2-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0013-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0015-5.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1071652" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0015-5-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0015-5-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0015-5-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0015-5.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>單方面暫停影片</h2><p>如果其中一個用戶需要去廁所而暫停了影片，GroupWatch 所有人的影片都會同時暫停。當影片再次播放時，所有人的影片都會重新播放。在時間軸上快轉到其他電影段落的操作也用類似方法同步，例如有一個人把時間軸移到去影片 2:00:00，所有人都會跳到這一秒同步播放。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0009-4.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1071669" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0009-4-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0009-4-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0009-4-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0009-4.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>自己帳戶用 GroupWatch 更簡單</h2><p>如果你是自己同自己玩 GroupWatch，即用同一個 Disney+ 帳戶且用同一個「使用者」，做法就會比較簡單。首先你在第一部裝置上，建立「GroupWatch」群組。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0037-scaled.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1071671" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0037-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0037-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0037-416x900.jpg 416w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0037-768x1661.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0037-710x1536.jpg 710w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0037-947x2048.jpg 947w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0037-scaled.jpg 739w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></a></p><p>然後打開另一部裝置的 Disney+ 應用程式，就會自動加入你自己建立的 GroupWatch 群組，只要點擊「加入群組」便可。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0048-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1071672" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0048-1-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0048-1-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0048-1-1200x900.jpg 1200w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0048-1-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/unwire0048-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=dFuQO2STV0k:4rHSzxOSM4M:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=dFuQO2STV0k:4rHSzxOSM4M:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>華為提供駕駛系統   AVATR 11 電動車中國發表</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/11/17/avatr-11-launched-in-china/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=avatr-11-launched-in-china</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[唐美鳳]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 17 Nov 2021 03:48:16 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[車壇動向]]></category><category><![CDATA[AVATR 11]]></category><category><![CDATA[寧德時代]]></category><category><![CDATA[華為]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1071808</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>早前我們報導過華為、寧德時代、長安汽車合作開發智能電動車，這款名叫 AVATR 11 的新車日前在上海正式發佈。中國傳媒以寧德時代提供電池和傳動系統，華為的軟件注入靈魂，長安汽車負責生產和銷售去形容 AVATR 11，新車採用由三家企業名字首個字母組成的 CHN 平台，在未來 5 年會推出 4 款型號。</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>早前我們報導過華為、寧德時代、長安汽車合作開發智能電動車，這款名叫 AVATR 11 的新車日前在上海正式發佈。中國傳媒以寧德時代提供電池和傳動系統，華為的軟件注入靈魂，長安汽車負責生產和銷售去形容 AVATR 11，新車採用由三家企業名字首個字母組成的 CHN 平台，在未來 5 年會推出 4 款型號。</p><p><span id="more-1071808"></span></p><p><a href="https://unwire.hk/2021/11/17/avatr-11-launched-in-china/life-tech/auto/attachment/1117-5c-3/" rel="attachment wp-att-1071819"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1071819" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1117-5c-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1117-5c-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1117-5c-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1117-5c.jpg 820w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>官方以轎跑 SUV 去定位 AVATR 11，車身由德國設計中心的德國團隊操刀，非常圓潤而沒有明顯稜角。AVATR 未有公佈詳細的規格配置，但就表示 AVATR 11 擁有最高可 700 公里的續航力（未有公佈基於哪個標準，估計是中國常用的 NEDC）。支援 200kW 以上的充電功率，而且 0 至 100 公里加速可以在 4 秒以下完成。</p><p><a href="https://unwire.hk/2021/11/17/avatr-11-launched-in-china/life-tech/auto/attachment/1117-5b-3/" rel="attachment wp-att-1071820"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1071820" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1117-5b-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1117-5b-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1117-5b-768x576.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1117-5b.jpg 820w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>AVATR 標榜新車擁有 400TOPS 的運算能力，AVATR 11 的 CDC 智能駕駛艙和 ADC 智能自動駕駛控制系統均由華為提供，除了可以實現高階智能駕駛，廠方還表示它具備人、車、家的無縫連接功能。AVATR 11 暫訂在 2022 年第三季交付，相信稍後會有更多有關此車的資訊公開。</p><p>來源：<a href="https://www.cnbeta.com/articles/tech/1203251.htm">cnbeta</a></p>
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=4jJo0NYp8vI:aqkT9aaRyaE:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=4jJo0NYp8vI:aqkT9aaRyaE:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>Kirin 9000 枯竭無法補充，華為旗艦被逼改用 Snapdragon 處理器</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/11/17/kirin-9000-are-running-out-huawei-forced-to-switch-to-snapdragon/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=kirin-9000-are-running-out-huawei-forced-to-switch-to-snapdragon</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[唐美鳳]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 17 Nov 2021 03:48:12 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[手提電話]]></category><category><![CDATA[Kirin 9000]]></category><category><![CDATA[qualcomm]]></category><category><![CDATA[華為]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1071807</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>中國傳媒日前報導指今年 7 月底發表的華為 P50 旗艦系列，可能會在 12 月起被逼全面改用 Qualcomm 處理器。由於自家 Kirin 9000 處理器庫存緊張，華為 P50 標準版和 P50 Pro 128GB 儲存版本一推出，就已經採用 Snapdragon 888 4G 處理器，而 P50 Pro 的 256GB 和 512GB 則採用 Kirin 9000。</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>中國傳媒日前報導指今年 7 月底發表的華為 P50 旗艦系列，可能會在 12 月起被逼全面改用 Qualcomm 處理器。由於自家 Kirin 9000 處理器庫存緊張，華為 P50 標準版和 P50 Pro 128GB 儲存版本一推出，就已經採用 Snapdragon 888 4G 處理器，而 P50 Pro 的 256GB 和 512GB 則採用 Kirin 9000。</p><p><span id="more-1071807"></span></p><p>當時華為曾經暗示會視乎情況，將原本採用 Kirin 9000 的型號都換成 Snapdragon 888 4G。雖然早在 7 月底發表，但華為一直未有將 P50 Pro 的 128GB 版推出，有中國科技博客日前爆料，表示 12 月起發售的 3 款不同容量 P50 Pro 都會改用 Snapdragon 888 4G 處理器。</p><p>中國傳媒指這代表 Kirin 9000 的庫存經已枯竭，同時華為還要留下一部份給未來的 Mate 50 系列使用。此外，有指華為 Mate X2 素皮版會在短期內發表，同樣採用 Kirin 9000 處理器。在受到美國制裁下，華為無法再向台積電採購 Kirin 9000 處理器，他們只可以在僅餘的庫存盡量調配，同時購買 Snapdragon 888 4G 去繼續推出新手機。</p><p>來源：<a href="https://m.cnbeta.com/view/1203209.htm">cnbeta</a></p>
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=Q7_8FYCHoho:bQjEoC-4lqA:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=Q7_8FYCHoho:bQjEoC-4lqA:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>舊款 Galaxy Watch 手錶，更新追加 Galaxy Watch 4 新功能</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/11/17/samsungs-older-smartwatches-are-getting-some-galaxy-watch4-features/life-tech/watch-wireless-home/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=samsungs-older-smartwatches-are-getting-some-galaxy-watch4-features</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[唐美鳳]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 17 Nov 2021 03:48:08 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[潮流手錶]]></category><category><![CDATA[Galaxy Watch]]></category><category><![CDATA[samsung]]></category><category><![CDATA[Tizen OS]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1071806</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>早前發表使用 Wear OS 3 的 Galaxy Watch4 系列智能手錶後，Samsung 未有忘記它們使用 Tizen 系統 Galaxy Watch 的老主顧，日前他們就宣佈為 Galaxy Watch、Galaxy Watch Active、Galaxy Watch Active2 和 Galaxy Watch3 推出更新，追加多項原本 Galaxy Watch4 獨有的功能。</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>早前發表使用 Wear OS 3 的 Galaxy Watch4 系列智能手錶後，Samsung 未有忘記它們使用 Tizen 系統 Galaxy Watch 的老主顧，日前他們就宣佈為 Galaxy Watch、Galaxy Watch Active、Galaxy Watch Active2 和 Galaxy Watch3 推出更新，追加多項原本 Galaxy Watch4 獨有的功能。</p><p><span id="more-1071806"></span></p><p><a href="https://unwire.hk/?attachment_id=1071824" rel="attachment wp-att-1071824"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1071824" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1117-3b-694x386.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="386" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1117-3b-694x386.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1117-3b-768x427.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1117-3b.jpg 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>Galaxy Watch Active2 和 Galaxy Watch3 用戶在更新後，可以獲得高靈敏度的跌倒偵測，當手錶感應到用戶可能跌到，就會發送 SOS 求救訊息予預設的聯絡人。容許用戶量度血壓和心電圖的 Samsung Health Monitor 程式，亦會在更新後支援上述兩款手錶，而且開放予更多市場使用。</p><p><a href="https://unwire.hk/?attachment_id=1071823" rel="attachment wp-att-1071823"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1071823" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1117-3c-694x386.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="386" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1117-3c-694x386.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1117-3c-768x427.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1117-3c.jpg 1000w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>此外，所有上述手錶型號在更新後，都會加入 Group Challenge 近年，讓用戶可以和朋友或家人共同挑戰，完成健康鍛煉目標。最後，Samsung 還將原本 10 款隨 Galaxy Watch4 推出的錶面設計，開放予上述所有 Tizen 系統的舊款 Galaxy Watch，用戶還可以自行更改背景和文字顏色。更新會率先向藍牙版手錶的美國和韓國用戶提供，其他市場和 LTE 版本的升級則會在稍後陸續提供。</p><p>來源：<a href="https://www.androidpolice.com/samsungs-older-smartwatches-are-getting-some-galaxy-watch4-features/">androidpolice</a></p>
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=ngPo-Z5TiAU:5_0eubccSTw:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=ngPo-Z5TiAU:5_0eubccSTw:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>日本電器品牌跨界推出手機   BALMUDA Phone 5G 手機發表</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/11/17/balmuda-phone-5g-launched/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=balmuda-phone-5g-launched</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[唐美鳳]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 17 Nov 2021 03:48:04 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[手提電話]]></category><category><![CDATA[Balmuda Phone]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1071805</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>以推出蒸氣多士爐馳名的日本家電品牌 BALMUDA，早前宣佈與 Kyocera 合作推出手機，他們首款 5G 手機 BALMUDA Phone 日前發表，有外國媒體直指是 2021 年最特別的手機。配備市場鮮見的 4.9 吋小屏幕和 138g 的輕巧細小機身，而且機背只有一個相機鏡頭。</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>以推出蒸氣多士爐馳名的日本家電品牌 BALMUDA，早前宣佈與 Kyocera 合作推出手機，他們首款 5G 手機 BALMUDA Phone 日前發表，有外國媒體直指是 2021 年最特別的手機。配備市場鮮見的 4.9 吋小屏幕和 138g 的輕巧細小機身，而且機背只有一個相機鏡頭。</p><p><span id="more-1071805"></span></p><p><a href="https://unwire.hk/?attachment_id=1071827" rel="attachment wp-att-1071827"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1071827" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1117-2b-694x404.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="404" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1117-2b-694x404.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1117-2b-768x447.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1117-2b.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>可以單手掌握和操控的 BALMUDA Phone，其 4.9 吋屏幕擁有 FHD 解像度，搭配 Qualcomm Snapdragon 765 處理器、6GB RAM 和 128GB 儲存，前置自拍鏡頭位 8MP，機背則有一枚 48MP 鏡頭，機背另一黑色的圓形物體是指紋辨識，弧形的塑料機背亦是 BALMUDA Phone 的特色之一。</p><p><a href="https://unwire.hk/?attachment_id=1071826" rel="attachment wp-att-1071826"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1071826" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1117-2c-694x285.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="285" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1117-2c-694x285.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1117-2c-768x316.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/1117-2c.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>BALMUDA Phone 內置 2,500mAh 電池，可以使用 USB-C 或以 Qi 標準無線充電，預載了 Android 11 系統和大量由 BALMUDA 開發的程式，包括相機、日曆、筆記和計算機等。BALMUDA Phone 由即日起在日本上市，售價 104,800 日元（約 7,119 港元），有黑、白兩色機身選擇。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.gsmarena.com/balmuda_phone_unveiled_with_49_display_pebbleshaped_design-news-51862.php">gsmarena</a></p>
